data.description: Welcome to this fabulous 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo located in the desirable 55+ community of Holiday Lake Villas. Situated on the first floor, this condo offers ease and convenience. Prepare to be impressed by the remodeled kitchen, featuring quartz countertops, soft close drawers, and stylish shaker white cabinets. The eat-in breakfast nook is perfect for casual dining, while the formal dining room provides an elegant space for entertaining guests. Step out onto the extra-large screened-in lanai and be captivated by the beautiful pond view, creating a serene and peaceful atmosphere for your morning coffee or evening relaxation. The split floor plan offers privacy, with the master bedroom boasting ample space, an en-suite bathroom, and a walk-in shower. The additional bedroom is also generously sized, accommodating guests or providing flexibility for a home office. This condo comes complete with an extra outdoor storage closet, ideal for storing seasonal items or outdoor gear.  Residents of this active 55+ community have access to a clubhouse with scheduled activities and clubs, offering plenty of opportunities to socialize and engage with neighbors. Dive into the very large pool for a refreshing swim or simply bask in the warm Florida sun. Conveniently located just minutes away from Tarpon Springs, you'll have a wide array of dining, shopping, and medical facilities within easy reach. Embrace the vibrant lifestyle this active adult community a has to offer while still enjoying the peace and tranquility of the tucked away location.  Most furnishings are included!  Don't miss out on the chance to own this exceptional condo Schedule a viewing today and start living the retirement you've always dreamed of. Seller is MOTIVATED! Schedule your appointment today!
